author: remm
msg: - Add new Manager.createSession(sessionId) method, allowing the client to "specify" the session id which should be used using a cookie
- This fixes session tracking when using emptySessionPath="true".
- The old createSession() method is deprecated.

author: remm
msg: - Improve a little logging of servlet exceptions, which should all log the root cause.
- Add a utility method in StandardWrapper.
- Don't log client aborts in the request dispatcher.

author: luehe
msg: Added StandardContext "processingTime" attribute, which provides the
cumulative processing times of all of the context's servlets
